data.description: This charming one-story home in a 55+ community is move-in ready and has desirable features. With tile floors throughout, hurricane-impact windows and doors, and a spacious living area, this home has it all. Complete with granite counters and backsplash, the kitchen is a true standout, and both bathrooms have been remodeled. Additionally, there is a large pantry and a full-size washer and dryer. A convenient side door leads to the carport to keep you dry while unloading groceries. The flexible family room at the back can serve as an office or even a third bedroom. The circuit breaker box was recently replaced. You can contact us now to schedule a viewing appointment. Easy to show.
